<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left;"><a href="/wiki/Category:Taxation_by_country" title="Category:Taxation by country">By country</a></div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center;"><a href="/wiki/Tax_rates_around_the_world" title="Tax rates around the world">Tax rates around the world</a><br />
